data.description: Back on Market due to buyer financing.  Welcome to your spacious and beautiful 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home, where comfort and style merge seamlessly. As you enter, the lovely hardwood floors in the spacious living room and dining room immediately catch your eye, setting the tone for the charm that awaits throughout. The refreshed kitchen boasts a new backsplash, adding a touch of modern flair to the heart of your home. Continuing the theme of hardwood flooring, the large family room is a welcoming space for relaxation and entertainment. The large laundry room, complete with cabinetry, and a convenient powder room contribute to the functional design of the home. The second floor will delight. The huge master bedroom features hardwood floors, a walk-in closet, and a dressing area. The master bathroom is a retreat in itself, offering a jacuzzi tub and a separate shower for luxurious pampering. The three additional bedrooms are generously sized, each equipped with great closets to accommodate your storage needs.  Step outside into your own backyard oasis. The gorgeous sunroom, flooded with natural light from numerous windows and skylights, is a perfect spot to relax year-round. The entire backyard is fenced with vinyl fencing for privacy and features an adorable she shed or man cave with air conditioning—an ideal escape for summer days spent by the newer inground pool. The addition of a fire pit adds a cozy touch for evening gatherings. Practical features abound, including a front yard sprinkler system, a security system for peace of mind, and a 3-year-old high-efficiency HVAC system. The roof was updated in 2010, ensuring durability and longevity. The 2-car garage and attic and 2 additional sheds provide ample storage space for your convenience. Embrace energy efficiency with solar panels that contribute to savings while being environmentally conscious.  Don't miss the opportunity to call this house your home—schedule a showing today and envision the possibilities that await!
